      "unit": "%",
      "note": "**擦伤级**的小口子，流得极慢，同样**永远流不死**。",
      "_id": "bleed_weight_micro",
      "_anchor": "src/DeadSignal.Combat/BleedModel.cs :: BleedModel.RateWeightOf",
